All Is Lost;;63;;94;;PG-13;;During a solo voyage in the Indian Ocean, a veteran mariner (Robert Redford) awakes to find his vessel taking on water after a collision with a stray shipping container. With his radio and navigation equipment disabled, he sails unknowingly into a violent storm and barely escapes with his life. With any luck, the ocean currents may carry him into a shipping lane -- but, with supplies dwindling and the sharks circling, the sailor is forced to face his own mortality.;;Drama,Adventure,Mystery & thriller;;J.C. Chandor;;2013;;Robert Redford;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/all_is_lost_2013